<article class="card card--horizontal"> <% if $FeaturedImage %> <div class="card__media"><a href="$Link" class=""><img src="$FeaturedImage.FocusFill(500,333).URL" class="card__img" loading="lazy" <% if $FeaturedImageAltText %> alt="$FeaturedImageAltText" <% else %> alt="$Title" role="presentation" <% end_if %>></a></div> <% end_if %> <div class="card__body"><h3 class="card__title"><a href="$Link">$Title</a></h3> <% if not $Parent.HideSummaries %> <% if $Summary %> <div class="card__summary">$Summary</div> <% else %> <p class="card__summary">$Content.FirstSentence</p><a href="$Link" class="button small hollow" aria-label="Continue reading about $Title">Continue Reading <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a> <% end_if %> <% end_if %> <% if $Categories.exists %> <p class=""> <% loop $Categories %> <a href="$Link" class="button small hollow black">$Title</a><% if not Last %><% else %><% end_if %> <% end_loop %> </p> <% end_if %> </div></article>